name: processing
description: [order, invoice] Status for actions having started and being processed

name: completed
description: [order] Status for order completed

name: deleted
description: [item] : Marks entity as deleted

name: refunded-restocked
description: [item, orderLineItem] : Entity has been completely refunded but restocked too

name: added
description: [orderItem] Status for orderItems that have been added to an order

name: created
description: [order, orderItem, fulfillment, invoice] The entity has been created

name: transit
description: [fulfillment, inventory] The entity is in transit

name: delivered
description: [fulfillment] The entity has been delivered

name: refunded
description: [order, orderItem] The entity has been refunded

name: pending

name: confirmed

name: fulfilling
description: [orderItem] The entity has been assigned to a fulfillment record

name: dispatched
description: [orderItem] The entity has been scanned out

name: rejected
description: [orderItem] Status of a rejected order line item

name: partially-dispatched
description: [order(outbound)] Some orderlineitems can still be dispatched

name: partially-confirmed
description: [order(outbound)]  Some orderlineitems can still be confirmed

name: partially-rejected
description: [order(outbound)] Some orderlineitems can still be rejected

name: partially-fulfilling
description: [order(inbound)] : Some orderlineitems can still be fulfilled

name: partially-arrived

name: arrived
description: [order(inbound)] : The entity is arrived

name: active
description: [inventory] : Active and selectable for action

name: drafted

name: voided

name: settled
description: [invoice] : Actions have been completed

description: [jobLineItem] Job Line Item has wrong location and is awaiting transfer

description: marketplace status to show that an entire listing has been claimed
